    <item>
      <title>Analytics Dashboard</title>
      <link>https://010101-sans.github.io/projects/analytics-dashboard/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 11:45:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://010101-sans.github.io/projects/analytics-dashboard/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;A comprehensive analytics dashboard for SaaS applications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;features&#34;&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Real-time data visualization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Custom report generation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced filtering and segmentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-user access control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data export capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;tech-stack&#34;&gt;Tech Stack&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Frontend&lt;/strong&gt;: React + D3.js&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Backend&lt;/strong&gt;: Go (Gin framework)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Database&lt;/strong&gt;: ClickHouse for time-series data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Caching&lt;/strong&gt;: Redis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;performance&#34;&gt;Performance&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Handles millions of events with sub-second query responses.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
